               stealing, on the <rs id="t18301209-4-cd20" type="crimeDate">3rd of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18301209-4-off19 t18301209-4-cd20"></join>, at St. Pancras, 1 cloak, value 7l., the goods of 
                     
